      <a href="/sources.html"><div class="tk">Provenance</div><div class="th">All sources →</div><div class="td">Every feed on the site, what it measures, its license, and when it last updated.</div></a>
    </div>
    <p class="srcnote">Sources for this section: <a href="https://www.inegi.org.mx" target="_blank" rel="noopener">INEGI</a> / CONEVAL (multidimensional poverty) · <a href="https://www.banxico.org.mx/SieInternet/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Banco de México (SIE)</a> / CONASAMI (minimum wage, remittances) · <a href="https://data.worldbank.org/country/mexico" target="_blank" rel="noopener">World Bank</a> (unemployment, population, GDP per capita) · CONAPO (population projection) · INEGI (registered births and deaths) · CNE / Sener (fuel prices).</p>
  </section>

